{
  "stem": "11184.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Just what an honor, what a beautiful thing to see a general that fought the war and made us free.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was just a feeling of undescribable feeling, really.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was so proud, you know, to see him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was just something, something to see that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was so happy that I got a picture, a guard, I don't know what the photographer, who he was.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But he said, I got pictures, do you want to buy some?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I got it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Mhm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now, when he said, do you want to buy some, how did you have money to buy anything?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know what we had.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had something, something was given to us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Food and-- and clothes was given to us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In a barracks.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were-- these used to be for the German soldiers, what you call, the barracks for the German soldiers.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we were there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were fed a meal every day, cooked meal.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I still remember that meal.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was rice with meat, what I would serve to 10 people today, what I would eat myself.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They got sick.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was-- this was later, a little later what I'm talking.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But at the beginning, they got so sick.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I saw people from the package only what we got from the Red Cross, people would eat up everything and got very, gravely ill and some died.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But me and my mother, we knew how to divide, because I-- that's why we survived, because we took one piece of bread and divide it.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You're not eating more than this one piece, so you have tomorrow another little piece.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the same thing I did with the package.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So it was easy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We didn't get sick.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
